Games organisers will be hoping, despite the coronavirus headaches,

33
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:30,520
despite the alleged human rights abuses, despite the allegations from a former Chinese Olympian,

34
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:34,680
a tennis star at that, involving a senior government official

35
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:38,640
that they can still produce a memorable Winter Olympics.

36
