So, at its highest level of activity, it's busiest.

38
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:52,560
And he mentioned the controversy surrounding the games.

39
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:57,320
Yes, he mentioned the coronavirus headache, not an actual headache,

40
