59
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:21,120
Stephen MacDonald describes this as a mountain of snow,

60
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:24,639
not a real mountain, but a larger amount of it.

61
00:04:24,639 --> 00:04:28,480
But some athletes say this type of snow is good for speed

62
