and changing and developing or dynamic conditions.

63
00:04:32,719 --> 00:04:36,480
They hope it will be a high-quality competition.

64
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:39,439
Let's hope so, and it's not long until it starts.

65
00:04:39,439 --> 00:04:45,120
